---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Lialvaro Custom Apparel Los Angeles">
  <section class="page-header text-center animate-up">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The story behind the print.</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-secondary" style="max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; font-size: 1.25rem;">Born in Los Angeles, Lialvaro Apparel was founded by artists who understand the power of a perfect garment.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section mt-4 pb-4">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="content-block animate-up delay-1">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We believe custom apparel shouldn't be complicated. Whether you're an independent creator needing a single prototype or a business outfitting a team of hundreds, our mission is to provide uncompromising quality with zero minimums.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block mt-4 animate-up delay-2">
        <h2>Why LA Chose Us</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We aren't a faceless factory. We're a local team deeply embedded in the Los Angeles creative community. We work with local organizations, support sustainable practices, and offer same-day turnarounds because we know this city never sleeps.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content-block mt-4 animate-up delay-3">
        <h2>Ethical & Sustainable</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Looking good shouldn't cost the earth. We're committed to sourcing eco-friendly garments and utilizing water-based, non-toxic inks whenever possible. Our process is designed to minimize waste without compromising on vibrancy or durability.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-4 pt-4 animate-up" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
        <h2>Start a new design project</h2>
        <a href="/contact" class="button family-quote-btn mt-2">Get a Free Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header { padding: 120px 0 60px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
  .content-section { padding-top: 6rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;}
  .content-block { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; margin-bottom: 5rem; }
  .content-block h2 { font-size: 2.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .content-block p { font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .family-quote-btn {
    background: #22856C !important;
    color: #fff !important;
  }
  .family-quote-btn:hover {
    background: #1b6f5a !important;
    color: #fff !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header { padding: 100px 0 40px; }
    .content-block h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .content-block p { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .content-block { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  }
</style>
